    • Estimate

      public Estimate​(java.lang.String idEstimate, float price, Client client, Advisor advisor, Car car, int period, java.util.List<Optional> optionalList, boolean visibility, java.lang.String state, java.util.Date requestDate, java.util.Date responseDate)
      Constructor for the Estimate Object.
      Parameters:
      idEstimate - is the ID who identifies the Estimate.
      price - is the price of the Estimate.
      client - is the client who requested the Estimate.
      advisor - is the advisor who compiled the Estimate.
      car - is the car for which the Estimate is required.
      period - is the time in month for which the car of the Estimate is required.
      optionalList - is the list of optionals that the Car shall have.
      visibility - tells you if the Estimate is still valid.
